**Requirements for Pick:**
- Extract only specified properties from an object type
- Accept a union of property keys as the second parameter
- Return a new type with only those properties

**Requirements for Omit:**
- Exclude specified properties from an object type
- Accept a union of property keys to exclude
- Return a new type without those properties

**Function signatures:**
typescript
type Pick<T, K extends keyof T> = {
  [P in K]: T[P];
};

